data.description: Spacious ranch home tucked away on a private lot. Step inside to neutral colors and high ceilings with updated flooring. Split bedroom plan offers privacy for guests or growing families. The kitchen hosts stainless steel appliances, granite counters and overlooks the living room. There is a formal dining room in addition to the eat-in kitchen area which can serve as a formal dining room or an office, additional living room area, play room etc. The master bedroom is generously sized and has a walk-in closet. The backyard is private and offers a deck to enjoy the outdoors which could easily be fenced in for pets. Don't miss the opportunity to own this well maintained home that is close to shopping, dining, and entertainment.
